reviewText: Not good. I don't recommend it. Janna Cova is the only one worth viewing and her outfit isn't special. The lighting is terrible.
Several good looking women showing all they have is hard to beat.  This one has Jana Cova as one of the five women.  She alone makes this tape worth the price.

Those of you who have grown up with Hot Body videos know exactly what to expect. Beautiful women in a softcore adult dvd. Full frontal and even closeups. The sad thing is that Hot Body is no longer producing new dvd's or VHS tapes and the prices are actually starting to rise. Check out ebay for some ridiculous bidding on Hot Body VHS tapes. When you find dvd's for less than $17 snatch them up. There aren't many out there and Sneaky Preview 68 is definitely one to grab.
